---
title: Hearty Chorizo, Mushrooms & Cherry Tomato Stew with Potato Mash, Leek & Parsley
description: Sit back and relax because this stew will come together in a flash. This bowl is like a warm hug with chorizo,
mushrooms and veggies simmered in tomato sauce and poured on top of a fluffy pile of mashed potatoes. There’s nothing better than a stew that can warm you from the inside out.

*Unfortunately, this week's silverbeet was in short supply, so we've replaced it with baby spinach. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious, just be sure to follow your recipe card!*
